thread.title_full: BRIEF-Nordic Semiconductor wins new order worth $3.2 million | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Nordic Semiconductor wins new order worth $3.2 million
text:
Sept 8 Nordic Semiconductor ASA :
* Has received new order for components to Consumer Electronics Market for total value of $3.2 million
* Says delivery of components will take place in Q3-Q4 2015
